{"tid":878510,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人玩秒服墨香(血海墨香)","createTime":"2018-10-27T08:01:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T08:52:46.000Z","uid":214693,"like":2,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"5f2c67fc96e0dba00ab7b804c99b934ed35a75e5","tid":878510,"uid":214693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T08:01:31.000Z","msg":"官網：<a href=\"http://www.msoxh.com/?fbclid=IwAR3BTQIRWhttSN4oHD5XbIe9dAs6Uekw81u9ztdGngNfuhfNLuqbRl-g6zc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.msoxh.com%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR3BTQIRWhttSN4oHD5XbIe9dAs6Uekw81u9ztdGngNfuhfNLuqbRl-g6zc&d=GeleZsKVHoltJkiQ0jbYIxv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=69f07ba3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.msoxh.com/?fbclid=IwAR3BTQIRWhttSN4oHD5XbIe9dAs6Uekw81u9ztdGngNfuhfNLuqbRl-g6zc</a><br />\n<br />\n1.人物經驗值1000% 技能點300% 掉寶率100% 武功經驗值2000%<br />\n2.最高等級為99級,每星期五會開放1轉,65級後可轉生,開服先開放3轉<br />\n3.本服目前最強裝備為祝福龍武+4,蠻牛套裝及天魔飾品。<br />\n4.玩家不但可以充值購買,更可以打王打怪取得。<br />\n(蚩牛巨靈會出天魔組合卷,打怪打副本可得到秘籍組合蠻牛套裝)<br />\n【祝福最大數值】<br />\n武器祝福值 : 攻擊(1~30)<br />\n首飾祝福值 : 力量、敏捷、心脈、體質(1~30)<br />\n防具祝福值 : 生命、護體、內力(10~1000)，防御力(10-200) ，屬性攻擊力20%<br />\n本服+1~+3設有安定值,玩家請使用多福卷組合,如因個人失誤導致物品粉碎,本服不會受理任何要求賠償<br />\n【泡點設置】<br />\n蘭州地圖每10分鐘獲得50泡點<br />\n其他地圖每10分鐘獲得30泡點<br />\n【遊戲特色】<br />\n本服只有滿滿的誠意和最認真的製作<br />\n●全新技能效果，全新特效，全新動態稱號<br />\n●語言功能因應玩家電腦系統轉繁/簡<br />\n●50惡名或以下(無論是否有榜)不爆裝備、不被搶奪物品、不跌武功<br />\n●新手註冊送1,000泡點，起手沒難度<br />\n●平衡各個職業，但各個職業都有好有壞，請自行比較哪個職業強才選擇<br />\n●刪除一人陣法，刪除R鍵連招，保障遊戲公平。<br />\n●開放查看對方屬性裝備和百寶符咒功能。<br />\n★血海墨香諮詢客服方法:<br />\nⓌ微信:hkmsogm<br />\nⓆQQ:864788486<br />\nⓁLINE:Hkmsogm<br />\n☎WhatsApp:852-63766961<br />\nⓆQQ群:927489178<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n是咁的 細佬課小小玩左依個墨香一排 個服開左10日到 我見活動都算OK GM派野都幾大方 <br />\n依加個服 有2個大盟 分別係殺手同惜玉 殺手係純大馬盟 可能有巴打玩過私服都見過佢地 惜玉就係香港人＋大馬人 依加惜玉同殺手日日打架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無巴打有興趣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2baf7bf9292ee57c267c9bd92dc68163b6a14959","tid":878510,"uid":9326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T12:54:17.000Z","msg":"留個名"},{"pid":"9ea9e013229872a466d338b6074f92dbefd763f2","tid":878510,"uid":214693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-27T18:08:29.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e91539c0c140f9e2c27448892d35d0557f71c56b","tid":878510,"uid":62022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"玩緊"},{"pid":"89bc1260eba9fa6f7caa431308589ea129a83385","tid":878510,"uid":214693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e91539c0c140f9e2c27448892d35d0557f71c56b","tid":878510,"uid":62022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T11:00:34.000Z","msg":"玩緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T16:29:26.000Z","msg":"巴打叫咩名"},{"pid":"07cb9760300d2e9da3b505510016bb50d83734ea","tid":878510,"uid":21569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T23:48:18.000Z","msg":"係咪同墨香冇分別不過所有野易達成左？"},{"pid":"7f46eb6098786506ea62c82ffc0b505c71a2f65a","tid":878510,"uid":9326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07cb9760300d2e9da3b505510016bb50d83734ea","tid":878510,"uid":21569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T23:48:18.000Z","msg":"係咪同墨香冇分別不過所有野易達成左？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T01:58:04.000Z","msg":"秒服姐係鬥點名技術 因為一整完裝就會秒到任何人"},{"pid":"67866376ab42eb9c6fb87278edc0fdcad32c8c60","tid":878510,"uid":214693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f46eb6098786506ea62c82ffc0b505c71a2f65a","tid":878510,"uid":9326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07cb9760300d2e9da3b505510016bb50d83734ea","tid":878510,"uid":21569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T23:48:18.000Z","msg":"係咪